Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.42,0:24:19.83,next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(450,320)\fad(100,100)}我要退出
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.01,0:24:20.51,next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(250,350)\fad(100,100)}果然到我了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.49,0:24:21.14,next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(450,350)\fad(100,100)}你們都做了些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.11,0:24:21.67,next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(250,320)\fad(100,100)}作戰進行得很順利
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.92,0:24:21.89,next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(450,320)\fad(100,100)}那是啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.32,0:24:23.11,next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(250,350)\fad(100,100)}我是1號哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.94,0:24:23.48,next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(450,350)\fad(100,100)}我們究竟在和什麼戰鬥啊
